The Free Edition is provided free of charge for personal, non-commercial use only. You may not use the Free Edition for any commercial purpose, including but not limited to providing services to third parties, integrating into commercial products, or generating revenue. All commercial use requires a paid Subscription (Pro, Enterprise, or Custom).

